					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The ".rodata" directive puts the string in the RODATA segment, which doesn't mix with the code. During linking, the assembler puts each segment's data into the file, as a contiguous chunk. Oh wait, I already put a comment to this effect. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

